'''Tasekla''' yekka-d seg wawal [[asekkil]] (tira umesli afraray), d ayen yaɛnan [[tira]], [[tajerrumt]], [[idles]]... Atg.

D tajruma n idrisen neɣ n wayen yakk yettwaqedcen ama s wudem n tira neɣ s win n watlay. Tasekla tamawit ar iqbayliyen, wala ar imaziɣen s umata, teǧhed. Ma d tasekla n tira, armi d timdi-agi taneggarut i bdan a ttarun. 

